<!-- === HERO === -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-content container">
    <h1 class="hero-heading" id="hero-heading">
      WEBSITES THAT <span class="accent">WORK</span> AS HARD AS YOU DO
    </h1>
    <div class="hero-glow" id="hero-glow"></div>
    <p class="hero-sub">Bespoke web design with 17+ years of design and marketing expertise behind every pixel.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="#portfolio" class="btn btn-primary">See My Work</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/442381112819" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp Me</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll-indicator">
    <div class="hero-scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === ABOUT === -->
<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image reveal-left">
        <div class="about-image-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/ryan-stanikk.jpg" alt="Ryan Stanikk - Web Designer and Commercial Photographer" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text reveal-right">
        <h4 class="about-label">About Me</h4>
        <h2>I build websites the way I shoot photos. With purpose.</h2>
        <p>I am Ryan Stanikk, a graphic designer with over 17 years in design and marketing, now channelling that expertise into building bespoke websites for businesses that want to stand out online.</p>
        <p>As a commercial photographer, I have spent years understanding what makes visuals work commercially, not just aesthetically. That same philosophy drives every website I build: it has to look stunning, but more importantly, it has to perform.</p>
        <p>Based in Southampton, working across the UK. I take in the full context of your business, your brand, your audience, and I craft something that reflects exactly who you are and what you need.</p>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">17+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in Design</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">4</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Live Projects</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">UK</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Wide Service</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === PORTFOLIO === -->
<section class="portfolio section" id="portfolio">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="reveal">My Work</h2>
      <a href="#contact" class="section-link reveal">Get Yours Built <span>&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>
    <p class="portfolio-intro reveal">Every project is designed to help a business grow. Here is a look at some of the websites I have crafted that drive results and make brands shine.</p>

    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      <div class="portfolio-card reveal">
        <div class="portfolio-card-image">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/padharo.jpg" alt="Padharo Restaurant Website" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="portfolio-card-overlay">
            <span class="tag">Restaurant</span>
            <a href="https://www.padharo.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Site <span>&rarr;</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="portfolio-card-title">Padharo</h3>
        <p class="portfolio-card-desc">Award-winning vegetarian Indian restaurant. Full multi-page site with reservation system, menus, and gallery.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-card reveal">
        <div class="portfolio-card-image">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/texas-grill.jpg" alt="Texas Grill Website" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="portfolio-card-overlay">
            <span class="tag">Restaurant</span>
            <a href="https://texas-grill.pages.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Site <span>&rarr;</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="portfolio-card-title">Texas Grill</h3>
        <p class="portfolio-card-desc">Bold, flavour-packed branding for a Southampton grill house. Menu integration, ordering, and strong visual identity.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-card reveal">
        <div class="portfolio-card-image">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/soleto.jpg" alt="Soleto Italian Restaurant Website" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="portfolio-card-overlay">
            <span class="tag">Restaurant</span>
            <a href="https://soleto-website.pages.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Site <span>&rarr;</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="portfolio-card-title">Soleto</h3>
        <p class="portfolio-card-desc">Refined Italian bistro with dark mode, gallery, private dining pages, and elegant typography throughout.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-card reveal">
        <div class="portfolio-card-image">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/ryanstanikk.jpg" alt="Ryan Stanikk Photography Website" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="portfolio-card-overlay">
            <span class="tag">Photography</span>
            <a href="https://www.ryanstanikk.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Site <span>&rarr;</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="portfolio-card-title">Ryan Stanikk Photography</h3>
        <p class="portfolio-card-desc">Commercial photography portfolio with searchable galleries, category navigation, and booking system.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === SERVICES === -->
<section class="services section" id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="reveal">What I Do</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="service-badge">Design</h4>
        <h3>Web Design</h3>
        <p>Bespoke websites built around your business. No templates, no cookie-cutter layouts. Every site is designed specifically for your brand and your audience.</p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Custom design</li>
          <li>Mobile-first</li>
          <li>Built to convert</li>
          <li>SEO foundations</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-card">Get Started</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="service-badge">Development</h4>
        <h3>Web Apps</h3>
        <p>More than just websites. I build functional web applications with the features your business needs, from content management to bespoke tools.</p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Custom web apps</li>
          <li>CMS integration</li>
          <li>Interactive features</li>
          <li>Performance-first</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-card">Get Started</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="service-badge">Infrastructure</h4>
        <h3>Hosting & Domains</h3>
        <p>I handle the technical side so you do not have to. Domain registration, hosting setup, SSL certificates, and ongoing maintenance all taken care of.</p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Domain registration</li>
          <li>Fast, secure hosting</li>
          <li>SSL certificates</li>
          <li>Ongoing support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-card">Get Started</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="service-badge">Content</h4>
        <h3>Content Management</h3>
        <p>Need to update your own content? I build systems that let you manage your site with ease. No technical knowledge required.</p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Easy editing</li>
          <li>No lock-in</li>
          <li>Training included</li>
          <li>Full control</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-card">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === PROCESS === -->
<section class="process section" id="process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="reveal">How I Work</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="process-number">01</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Discovery</h3>
          <p>I dig into your business, your brand, your audience, and your goals. I look at everything from your existing materials to your competitors to understand what will work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-line"></div>

      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="process-number">02</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Design</h3>
          <p>With the mind of a graphic designer and the eye of a photographer, I craft layouts that reflect exactly who you are. Every element is intentional.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-line"></div>

      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="process-number">03</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Build</h3>
          <p>Clean, fast, accessible code. I build for performance and SEO from the ground up, making sure your site works flawlessly on every device.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-line"></div>

      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="process-number">04</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Launch</h3>
          <p>Domain connected, hosting configured, SSL live, everything tested. I handle the entire deployment so you can focus on your business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-line"></div>

      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="process-number">05</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Support</h3>
          <p>I do not disappear after launch. Ongoing support, updates, and maintenance to keep your site performing at its best.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === FAQ === -->
<section class="faq section" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="reveal">Common Questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How much does a website cost?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Every project is different. The cost depends on the scope, number of pages, features needed, and complexity. I am always transparent about pricing and will give you a clear breakdown before any work starts. Get in touch for a no-obligation chat.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How long does it take to build a website?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>A typical single-page site can be ready in 1 to 2 weeks. Larger multi-page sites or sites with custom features may take 3 to 6 weeks. I will give you a realistic timeline during our initial conversation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Do I need to provide content and images?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>I take in everything you have: documents, existing websites, social media, images, videos. As a commercial photographer, I can also create imagery for your site. I will work with whatever materials you have and fill in the gaps.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Will I be able to update the site myself?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>If you need a content management system, I can build one into your site. You will be able to update text, images, and content without any technical knowledge. I also provide training on how to use it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Do you handle hosting and domains?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. I can register a new domain for you or connect your existing domain to the new site. Hosting is arranged as part of the build. You own everything and there is no lock-in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What about complex features like e-commerce?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>I can build e-commerce systems and complex web applications. For highly complex features, we will have a conversation about scope and pricing upfront so there are no surprises. I am always straightforward about what is involved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === CONTACT CTA === -->
